name: STOP PUTIN SAVE UKRAINE
description:
Original work by a contemporary Ukrainian artist Eugene Gorbachenko

MONEY FROM SALE GOES TO SUPPORT UKRAINE

The war in Ukraine has been going on since 2014. After the revolution, Russia viciously attacked Ukraine and annexed Crimea and two regions. Recently, on February 24, 2022, Russia launched a full-scale open war against Ukraine. Our heroes bravely defend their land. Ukraine will win. Glory to Ukraine!
